Sara woke up, and then looked around. She was back home, and nothing looked destroyed. She walked into Plazmus' room. Then she gasped. What did he do? "Plazmus! Get away from there!" she yelled, before finally pulling him away from the protractor. She turned to him. "What did you do?"

"I completed a project," said Plazmus, "aren't you proud of me?" Sara knew he was trying to get out of trouble. This 'project' was not safe.

"That could have KILLED you!" she yelled, "and I don't want to lose my brother!"
